SUMMARY:Lec64|Decoder for quantum error correction codes: from the perspective of classical error correction codes|Tzu-Hsuan Huang-National Tsing Hua University
LOCATION:https://tinyurl.com/gucs-zoom
DESCRIPTION:Quantum error correction has become a crucial and popular topic\, especially given its essential role in ensuring the scalability and reliability of quantum computers. In this talk\, I will introduce quantum error correction from a classical error correction perspective. Additionally\, I will present our work on developing decoders for quantum codes.
